OL,6,GThere are times when someone who cares
OL,7,Gabout TV should be keeping across the
OL,8,Gbusiness news.
OL,10,FIn recent weeks, there's been intense
OL,11,Fspeculation about the possibility of a
OL,12,Fbid for ITV plc.
OL,14,FSo far nothing has come of it but, as
OL,15,Fis usually the way, the speculation
OL,16,Fhas boosted the company's share price.
OL,18,FSome city analysts have spoken of a
OL,19,F"break up" bid for the company.
OL,21,FThis basically suggests that ITV plc
OL,22,Fis undervalued by the stock market.
