OL,6,FIts two separate divisions ` ITV
OL,7,FStudios and the consumer business
OL,8,Fwhich runs the channels ` would be
OL,9,Fseparately owned if such a move were
OL,10,Fto happen.
OL,12,FFor absolute clarity, a break up would
OL,13,Fnot mean a return to the old ITV
OL,14,Fregional structure. There is no
OL,15,Fsuggestion of "breaking up" the
OL,16,Fbroadcasting business into separate
OL,17,Fregional companies again.
OL,19,FRather there would be two entirely
OL,20,Fseparate businesses.
