OL,6,
OL,7,F The operation currently known as ITV
OL,8,FStudios. It makes the bulk of ITV's
OL,9,Fprogrammes and wins commissions from
OL,10,Fother broadcasters. It also sells
OL,11,Fprogrammes and formats internationally.
OL,12,F The consumer business which trades
OL,13,Fdirectly with the public. This runs
OL,14,Fthe broadcast channels and ITV X.
OL,16,FThe idea that a commercial public
OL,17,Fservice broadcaster need not have any
OL,18,Fsignificant programme making capacity
OL,19,Fof its own is not unusual ` Channel 4
OL,20,Fand Channel 5 commission all their
OL,21,Fprogrammes from independent production
OL,22,Fcompanies.
