OL,6,FWhether this would make long-term
OL,7,Fsense for ITV is a different question.
OL,9,FUltimately the commercial importance
OL,10,Fof linear channels is declining.
OL,12,FIn fact, for anyone who cares about
OL,13,Ftelevision in society, the problems
OL,14,Fwhich have faced major broadcasters in
OL,15,Frecent years should be a major concern.
OL,17,FPressure on budgets has meant fewer
OL,18,Fcommissions and a greater degree of
OL,19,Frisk aversion. It is not hard to see
OL,20,Fwhy some in independent production and
OL,21,Fcommercial broadcasting worry that the
OL,22,Findustry is dying.
