OL,6,FWhat is genuinely concerning though is
OL,7,Fthat there seem to be occasions when
OL,8,FITV 1 now puts up the white flag and
OL,9,Faccepts that BBC One is going to
OL,10,Fdominate.
OL,12,FAs a big supporter of the BBC, you
OL,13,Fmight think I would be happy about
OL,14,Fthis. Actually I'm not.
OL,16,FWhile I love to see the BBC win ` and
OL,17,Fthe corporation must never use ratings
OL,18,Fas the sole judge of success ` the
OL,19,Fviewing public benefits from
OL,20,Fcompetition and choice.
